= Conclusion
At the end of this booklet, I turn to Allāh with praise and thanks for the success and ease He has granted.
I hope this book has helped clarify the concept of Tawḥīd (monotheism), contributed to simplifying its rulings, and made its topics more accessible.
I also ask Allāh, the Most High and Almighty, to grant the best reward to all those who contributed in printing and distribution of this booklet, and to greatly increase their reward and blessings.
May Allāh’s peace and blessings be upon our Prophet Muḥammad, and upon his family and companions.

Abdullah bin Ahmad Al-Huwail